## Risk Assessment

- **HIGH**: Adding grade_id to classes is a new FK that all class queries must respect. Existing class queries assume campus-level scope only.
- **HIGH**: Data migration heuristics — inferring grade from class names may not always work. Needs manual review path.
- **MEDIUM**: JWT claim size increase. Adding grade_id is minimal but token refresh logic must handle null case.
- **LOW**: Frontend changes are additive — new dropdown, no breaking changes to existing UI.
